  for (let i = 0; i < targetCount; i++) {
    const prompt = `
🎯 LIFESTYLE MOCKUP PROMPT (Image ${i + 1}/5)

PROMPT:
Create a photorealistic lifestyle mockup image for "${keyword}" Acrylic Ornament using the exact design I provide.
Each image must depict the Ornament in a different realistic lifestyle context, while strictly preserving the original design.

Core requirements (NON-NEGOTIABLE):
The Ornament must be true-to-scale, real-world accurate size, perfectly matching the original product dimensions.
The Ornament must appear as a real physical Acrylic Ornament (2D printed), naturally placed or attached to a suitable surface.
No resizing, no stretching, no warping, no floating.
The design must be:
perfectly centered
extremely sharp and high-resolution
correct original colors & layout
clean edges, no wrinkles, no distortion
fully visible (100% of design shown)
Do NOT add or modify any text, logo, watermark, or graphic.

Placement:
Apply the provided design only to the correct Ornament print area / label position.
Ornament must not touch human skin and must not be worn.

📸 Lifestyle Context:
Scene theme: ${insight.context}. (Variation ${i + 1}: Ensure this angle is unique).
The Ornament is always the hero subject.

👤 Characters (if any):
Subject: ${insight.persona} (Human presence must be subtle/blurry, never blocking product).
Action: natural, candid interaction that helps clearly showcase the Ornament.

🎭 Mood & Vibe:
${insight.mood}
Natural, emotional, lifestyle-driven, commercial-ready.

🧰 Props:
${insight.props}
Props must only support the scene.
Must NOT cover, overlap, or distract from the Ornament.
No copyrighted brand names, logos, or readable brand text.

💡 Lighting & Camera:
Realistic lighting matching the environment
Natural shadows and reflections
No glare or light bloom covering the design
Cinematic depth of field
35mm lens look
Shallow DOF
Clean bokeh background

🎬 Composition & Quality:
Commercial lifestyle photography
Rule of thirds
Clear hero focus on the Ornament
Ultra-realistic, high detail
Natural color grading
High resolution, print-ready
No background clutter

🚫 NEGATIVE PROMPT (GIỮ NGUYÊN & MỞ RỘNG):
blurry, low quality, warped Ornament, distorted design, unreadable text, wrong colors,
